Package: cytoverse
Title: Easily Install and Load the 'cytoverse'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Mike",
             family = "Jiang",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "wjiang2@fredhutch.org"))
Description: The 'cytoverse' is a set of packages that are commonly used for cytometry data analysis. 
            This package is designed to make it easy to install and load
    multiple 'cytoverse' packages in a single step.
